      "message": "Patch Set 1: (2 inline comments)\n\nI suspect the real code that is failing is this:\n        rc = mdt_object_exists(parent);\n        if (unlikely(rc == 0)) {\n                LU_OBJECT_DEBUG(D_WARNING, info->mti_env,\n                                &parent->mot_obj.mo_lu,\n                                \"Parent doesn't exist!\\n\");\n                RETURN(-ESTALE);\n\nSince for attr by fid case parentfid is the same as child, we'd mail out early on on this check, no?",
